{"id":6571,"date":"2026-04-21T14:17:32","date_gmt":"2026-04-21T14:17:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/?page_id=6571"},"modified":"2026-04-26T15:48:37","modified_gmt":"2026-04-26T15:48:37","slug":"partners-institutions","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/partners-institutions\/","title":{"rendered":"Partners &#038; Institutions"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"6571\" class=\"elementor elementor-6571\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-06f4540 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"06f4540\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7febe8c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7febe8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Partners &amp; Institutions<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e614ac elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6e614ac\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Building Global Partnerships to Power Agriculture<\/p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11e70a61 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"11e70a61\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-484d84d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"484d84d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Creating Measurable Impact<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-60b1c30a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"60b1c30a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"238\" data-end=\"524\">Our mission is powered by a global network of partners and institutions committed to transforming agriculture, strengthening rural economies, and improving lives. By working together, we combine expertise, resources, and innovation to deliver scalable, measurable impact across regions.<\/p><p data-start=\"556\" data-end=\"642\">We collaborate with a diverse range of stakeholders across the agricultural ecosystem:<\/p><p data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"859\"><strong data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"671\">Government Institutions<\/strong><br data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"674\" \/>Partnering with national and regional governments to design and implement large-scale agricultural and rural development programs aligned with policy frameworks and national priorities.<\/p><p data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"1067\"><strong data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"899\">International Organizations &amp; NGOs<\/strong><br data-start=\"899\" data-end=\"902\" \/>Working alongside global development organizations to deliver high-impact initiatives focused on food security, nutrition, sustainability, and community empowerment.<\/p><p data-start=\"1069\" data-end=\"1294\"><strong data-start=\"1069\" data-end=\"1107\">Financial Institutions &amp; Investors<\/strong><br data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1110\" \/>Collaborating with banks, development funds, and private investors to unlock financing for farmers, cooperatives, and agribusiness projects\u2014driving growth and long-term sustainability.<\/p><p data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1493\"><strong data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1332\">Academic &amp; Research Institutions<\/strong><br data-start=\"1332\" data-end=\"1335\" \/>Partnering with universities and research centers to integrate innovation, data, and scientific expertise into training, production, and development programs.<\/p><p data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1696\"><strong data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1530\">Private Sector &amp; Agribusinesses<\/strong><br data-start=\"1530\" data-end=\"1533\" \/>Connecting with companies across the agricultural value chain to create market opportunities, strengthen supply chains, and drive commercial success for producers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6135006e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6135006e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b3f8a36 elementor-widget elementor-widget-cherito-about\" data-id=\"2b3f8a36\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"cherito-about.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"about-one section-space\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"about-one__bg\"><\/div><!-- \/.about-one__bg -->\r\n\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row gutter-y-50\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"sec-title wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"sec-title__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA Unified Ecosystem\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3><!-- \/.sec-title__title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.sec-title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__text-box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"about-one__text\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOur platform brings partners together within a single, integrated ecosystem whe